\c 7
\s Kunyengedzera kwechifeve
\p
\v 1 Mwanakomana wangu, chengetedza mashoko angu, nemirairo yangu uvige kwauri.
\v 2 Chengetedza mirairo yangu ugorarama, nemurau wangu semboni yemaziso ako.
\v 3 Uzvisungire paminwe yako; uzvinyore pahwendefa remoyo wako.
\v 4 Uti kuuchenjeri: Uri hanzvadzi yangu; utumidze kunzwisisa \add kuti\add* hama.
\v 5 Kuti zvikuchengetedze pamukadzi wekumwe, pamukadzi mutorwa anobata kumeso nemashoko ake.
\p
\v 6 Nokuti ndakatarira pahwindo reimba yangu, pautanda hwehwindo rangu.
\v 7 Zvino ndakaona pakati pevasina mano, ndikacherekedza pakati pevechidiki jaya rakashaiwa njere;
\v 8 richipfuura munhandare yemumusha pedo nekona yake, richifamba nenzira yeimba yake;
\v 9 parubvunzavaeni, pamadekwani ezuva, parima reusiku kwakasviba.
\v 10 Zvino tarira, mukadzi wakamuchingamidza, \add ane\add* chipfeko chechifeve, neunyengeri pamoyo.
\v 11 Ane ruzha, uye wakasindimara; tsoka dzake hadzigari mumba make.
\v 12 Iyezvi ari panze, iyezvi ari munhandare dzemumusha, uye anovandira pakona imwe neimwe.
\v 13 Zvino anoribata, ndokuritsvoda, ndokuomesa chiso chake, ndokuti kwariri:
\v 14 Zvibairo zvezvipo zvekuyananisa zviri kwandiri; nhasi ndaripa mhiko dzangu.
\v 15 Naizvozvo ndabuda kukuchingamidza, kutsvakisisa chiso chako; zvino ndakuwana.
\v 16 Ndakawarira mubhedha wangu nemachira ane ukomba, micheka yakapfava ine mavara inobva Egipita.
\v 17 Ndakasasa mubhedha wangu nemura, gavakava, nekinamoni.
\v 18 Uya, tizvigutse nerudo rukuru kusvika mangwanani; tizvifadze nekudanana kukuru.
\v 19 Nokuti murume haapo mumba make; wakafamba rwendo kure.
\v 20 Wakatora hombodo yemari muruoko rwake; pazuva rejenaguru achadzoka kumba kwake.
\v 21 Anoritsausa nekuwanda kwedzidziso yake; anorigombedzera nekubata kumeso kwemiromo yake.
\v 22 Pakarepo rinomutevera senzombe ichienda kunobaiwa, uye se\add ari\add* muzvisungo kuenda pakurangwa;
\v 23 kusvika museve watsemura chiropa chake; seshiri inokurumidzira kurudzingi, uye isina kuziva kuti rwunorwisa upenyu hwayo.
\p
\v 24 Naizvozvo ikozvino, imwi vana, inzwai kwandiri, muteerere kumashoko emuromo wangu.
\v 25 Moyo wako ngaurege kutsaukira kunzira dzake; usadzungaira mumakwara ake.
\v 26 Nokuti akawisira pasi vazhinji vakakuvadzwa; nevose vakaurawa vake vakawanda.
\v 27 Imba yake inzira dzegehena, dzinoburukira kumakamuri erufu.